name: Protobuf
description:
IntelliJ-based IDEs Protobuf Language Plugin that provides Protobuf language support.

Analyzing features:

  • Syntax highlighting
  • Symbol and References
  • Import file from library and SDK
  • Navigation
  • Find Usage
  • Code folding
  • Semantic analysis
  • Struct Viewer

Editor features:

  • Auto Completion
  • Code format
  • Import optimizing
  • AIP spec support
  • PSI stub
  • Auto import
